      <textAnnotation id="sid-01F555F1-C9A1-428D-84D3-754F4F4662E6" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="" fontFamily="" fontSize="20.0" italic="" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="" fontFamily="" fontSize="20.0" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process tower: OTC-Order To Cash
Process Group: O-Order Management
Process: O-020-160F Determine Order Price and Conditions</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-B6594EA8-5DA1-4A70-904D-ED1FE3DFEE91" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1)SIMS Process with IP and External Customer
 2)Cost from Material master is loaded to Condition ZPRS or ZCST.
3)Mark up ZMRK will be added taking the cost as the Basis
OR
If ZCPR/ZMPR/ZCIP is available - The same is prioritized 
4)Mark Up is loaded by Price analyst.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
